source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_000<tab>By reconditioning the Resistance weapon, you can redistribute the attribute points allocated to your weapon.
target: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_000<tab>By reconditioning the Resistance weapon, you can redistribute the attribute points allocated to your weapon.

source:
TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_MEMORIZESYSTEM_000_001Reapplication of aetheroinsulation coating requires phials of aetherial sealant.
House of Splendors representatives are standing by, and ready to take your order!
target:
TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_MEMORIZESYSTEM_000_001Reapplication of aetheroinsulation coating requires phials of aetherial sealant.
House of Splendors representatives are standing by, and ready to take your order!

source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_002<tab>Aetherial sealant can be obtained from Auriana at Revenant's Toll or Hismena at Idyllshire.
target: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_002<tab>Aetherial sealant can be obtained from Auriana at Revenant's Toll or Hismena at Idyllshire.

source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_150<tab>By supplying the Allagan node with aetherial sealant, you may raise the four available attributes of your Resistance weapon as you see fit.
target: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_150<tab>By supplying the Allagan node with aetherial sealant, you may raise the four available attributes of your Resistance weapon as you see fit.

source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_151<tab>When you are satisfied with the allotment of attributes, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Allocate<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> to complete the process.
target: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_151<tab>When you are satisfied with the allotment of attributes, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Allocate<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> to complete the process.

source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_152<tab>Choose carefully, as redistribution of attributes will require the procurement of additional sealant.
target: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_152<tab>Choose carefully, as redistribution of attributes will require the procurement of additional sealant.

source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_MEMORIZESYSTEM_000_190<tab><blip> <blip> Unable to process request. Insufficient aetherial sealant.
target: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_MEMORIZESYSTEM_000_190<tab><blip> <blip> Unable to process request. Insufficient aetherial sealant.

source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_MEMORIZESYSTEM_000_200<tab><blip> <blip> Unable to process request. Incompatible weapon detected. Please verify the correct weapon is equipped before placing next request.
target: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_MEMORIZESYSTEM_000_200<tab><blip> <blip> Unable to process request. Incompatible weapon detected. Please verify the correct weapon is equipped before placing next request.

source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_210<tab>You may only recondition your currently equipped Resistance weapon when accessing the Allagan node.
target: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_210<tab>You may only recondition your currently equipped Resistance weapon when accessing the Allagan node.

source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_MEMORIZESYSTEM_000_300<tab><blip> Suspending weapon recondition protocol. Entering standby mode...
target: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_MEMORIZESYSTEM_000_300<tab><blip> Suspending weapon recondition protocol. Entering standby mode...

Reapplying aetheroinsulation coating...
Reconditioning protocol complete.

source: TEXT_LUCKSA299_04041_SYSTEM_000_601<tab>The Resistance weapon has been transformed, gaining newfound strength!
